            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="item active">
                    <section class="page-block">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h2>YES, You Can Load Personal Items In Your Vehicle</h2>
    </div>

    <br><br>
    
    <div class="row">
        
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3">
                    <i class="icon icon-travel-bag icon-box gradient-orange"></i>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-9">
                    <h4>One Suitcase</h4>
                    <p>With Montway you can have 1 suitcase or bag of up to <strong>100 lbs.</strong> in the trunk free of charge</p>
                    <div class="visible-lg"><br></div>
                    <div class="visible-md"><br><br></div>
                </div>
            </div>
                     
            <div class="callout callout-warning">
                <p><i class="fa fa-info-circle fa-fw"></i> Anything over 100 lbs. can compromise the weight restrictions trucks must follow.<br><br><br><br></p>
            </div>
        </div>      <!-- left column -->
        
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3">
                    <i class="icon icon-box-label icon-box gradient-purple"></i>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-xs-9">    
                    <h4>Loading Extra Items</h4>
                    <p>If you want to add more than 100 lbs. of items in your vehicle, <strong>$100 or more</strong> is added to your total cost depending on the size of your car. The smaller the vehicle, the lower the cost.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="callout callout-default">
                <p><i class="fa fa-info-circle fa-fw"></i> <strong>If you choose this option, please know that:</strong></p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>you may load belongings inside the vehicle and the trunk</li>
                    <li>items MUST be loaded below window level</li>
                    <li>the driverâ€™s seat MUST be clear at all times</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>      <!-- right column -->
        
    </div>      <!-- .row -->

    <hr>
    <br>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h4>Please understand the risks of shipping personal items in your car.</h4>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <ul>
                <li>not insured</li>
                <li>at risk for theft</li>
                <li>may cause damage to the interior of your vehicle (these damages are not insured by Montway)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <ul>
                <li>not the responsibility of the truck driver</li>
                <li>can compromise the weight limitations</li>
                <li>can damage car suspension</li>
                <li>may cause damage to the undercarriage due to extra weight</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>


<div class="callout callout-success">
    <p><i class="fa fa-info-circle fa-fw"></i> Every truck driver is subject to inspection at state lines and can be fined for hauling personal items as the "Federal and State Department of Transportation (DOT) regulations prohibit the transport of household items in vehicles being transported by auto carriers.</p>
</div>


<div class="callout callout-danger">
    <p><i class="fa fa-info-circle fa-fw"></i> Under NO circumstances are Explosives, Guns, Ammunition, Flammable Products, Narcotics or any unlawful contraband allowed in your vehicle during transport.</p>
</div>                </div>
            </div>      <!-- .carousel-inner -->
        
        </div>      <!-- .carousel -->
        
